{"tid":1350830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[夢幻國度]石門陳根記,點去迪士尼?","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:05:31.000Z","uid":69650,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64a17352fa9c1904e4959f1e8c59204c874c159b","tid":1350830,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:51:15.000Z","msg":"琴晚發夢,夢見老鼠<br />\n唯有每日定時開超聲波趕老鼠,每朝返工經過石門2期既打工仔日日都聽到知咩事<br />\n朝早開到下午4點,5點接客凌晨收工再開過<br />\n搞到格黎幾間餐廳雞犬不寧,早餐中午時段d人走撚哂<br />\nbtw迪士尼我最中意就係丁滿同彭彭<br />\n彭彭就最中意做管理員,好似最大粒個個<br />\n唔知佢幫唔幫到手呢"},{"pid":"46522befcbd9d5337f8a7230d6eb9a22e7531b4a","tid":1350830,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:51:58.000Z","msg":"btw中左毒要點?<br />\n自行解毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"8a73f5e507a6e213b5c768ba9a07874c3bdb16a3","tid":1350830,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"有冇石門打工仔傾計下?"},{"pid":"707b9b58696dcb1f08bc2e893632e04a009be2cc","tid":1350830,"uid":76200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:00:07.000Z","msg":"放工經過去睇，拉左閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3184aaae31c22618e245368336f3cad321ead49","tid":1350830,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b4d5b743c6a1e0257ea8f3dd0deb7a6a8cb2567","tid":1350830,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c20743bb4ed8c783a91b6be4ceaa7cce6e7c645","tid":1350830,"uid":117304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾尼架陳根記，野又難食，個老細周恆又閪。"}]}